OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772773445
OL,3,CWet February leads to plunge in
OL,4,Cshopping trips
OL,6,FFootfall decreased year-on-year across
OL,7,Fall nations, down 2.3% in Northern
OL,8,FIreland, 3% in Scotland, 5% in England
OL,9,Fand 5.8% in Wales.
OL,11,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,12,Fsaid: "One of the wettest Februarys on
OL,13,Frecord saw shoppers shy away from in-
OL,14,Fstore visits last month.
OL,16,F"Footfall was down across all
OL,17,Flocations, with high streets and
OL,18,Fshopping centres hit hardest ` a blow
OL,19,Ffelt most keenly by clothing and
OL,20,Ffootwear retailers."
