OL,3,CWet February leads to plunge in
OL,4,Cshopping trips
OL,6,FAndy Sumpter, from Sensormatic, said:
OL,7,F"February proved a more challenging
OL,8,Fmonth for UK retail, with footfall
OL,9,Fslipping further into decline and
OL,10,Freversing the tentative progress seen
OL,11,Fin January.
OL,13,F"Exceptionally heavy rainfall ` well
OL,14,Fabove the seasonal average ` kept
OL,15,Fshoppers away from high streets and
OL,16,Fretail destinations, driving a natural
OL,17,Fshift towards online shopping as
OL,18,Fconsumers chose convenience and
OL,19,Fshelter from the downpours.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
