OL,3,CWet February leads to plunge in
OL,4,Cshopping trips
OL,6,F"Economic pressures added an extra
OL,7,Flayer of strain. Continued food price
OL,8,Finflation and rising unemployment
OL,9,Fcontinued to weigh on household
OL,10,Fbudgets, making both discretionary
OL,11,Ftrips and discretionary spending
OL,12,Feasier to delay."
